#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-birds-from-literature.adoc:115
msgid "Take the role of a volunteer charged with transforming the translated text into a spreadsheet as individual occurrences.  The occurrences will need unique numbers assigned to them."
msgstr "請扮演一位負責將翻譯文本轉換為個別出現紀錄的志工，這些出現紀錄需要分配唯一編號。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-birds-from-literature.adoc:116
msgid "Create a spreadsheet using the data fields listed in the <<birds-digital-data-description>> using data found in the example above recorded by: Chr. Fr. Lütken."
msgstr "請使用上述範例中由 Chr. Fr. Lütken 記錄的資料，並根據 《birds-digital-data-description》 中列出的資料欄位建立試算表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-birds-from-literature.adoc:117
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:86
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-marine.adoc:25
msgid "Use the exercise sheet to provide your answers and submit the spreadsheet created in the previous step."
msgstr "請使用練習表格填寫你的答案，並提交於前一步驟中建立的試算表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-birds-from-literature.adoc:119
msgid "In the examples used, the individual occurrences do not always contain data to complete all of the columns in the spreadsheet."
msgstr "在使用的範例中，個別的出現紀錄並不總是包含完整的試算表欄位資料。"

